data.name: ReadOfficeServiceProviderAlert
data.value: select top(1) SYSTEM_GENERATED_I, OPTIMIZED_FLAG from CKT_OSP_ALERT where SYSTEM_GENERATED_I = @systemGeneratedI

data.name: UpdateOfficeServiceProviderAlert
data.value: update CKT_OSP_ALERT set OPTIMIZED_FLAG = @optimizedFlag where SYSTEM_GENERATED_I = @systemGeneratedI
